name: Mug Rug
description:
The Mug Rug is the perfect place to rest your coffee and snack during any coffee break.  

Each Mug Rug is quilted with a layer of batting between fun designer quilting cotton.  They are machine washable and have been preshrunk.

Each Mug Rug is approximately 10" square and pattern placement / material may differ slightly.

name: Craft Kit
description:
The Craft Kit is packed with bright and fun craft supplies to bring out the creativity in every child.  

Craft Kits make a great gift for birthdays, Christmas, new big brother/sisters or just because.  

They are the perfect size for little ones to carry with them when visiting friends, out to restaurants or anywhere else they need something to do.

Each kit contains:
card stock, crepe paper, feathers, buttons, pipe cleaners, scissors, glue, wash tape, crayons, blank note pad, pom poms, embroidery floss, gimp, iron on patches & popsicle sticks all packed in a mini suitcase.

{Please note there are small items that are not intended for small children}

name: Purple & White Bakers Twine
description:
Bakers Twine...it is one hardworking additon to any creative cupboard.

Perfect for crafting, scrapbooking and stationary (think banners, pompoms and cards).  Wrap around a pretty gift or some yummy baked goods.  Add a mini bunting to a (premade) ;) cake and you have a fabulous desert.

You will receive 25 yards of bakers twine handwrapped around a recycled tag.

Other colours available:

Navy & White
Light Blue & White
Red & White
Pink & White
Yellow & White
Bright Blue & White

For more craft ideas to use with your Bakers Twine, visit my Pinterest board here: http://pinterest.com/jules647/twine/

name: Growth Chart Ruler
description:
This oversized Growth Chart is a fun way to track how much your children are growing.  The best part is it is portable which means your memories won't be lost if you move or decide to paint your wall.

The Growth Chart Ruler has been hand stained, painted and protected.

There is a sawtooth hanger attached to the back for easy hanging - 6" off the ground for an accurate measurement.

The Perfect iPad Cover is handcrafted using high quality quilting fabric.  It has a layer of padding for protection as well as a soft flannel lining to prevent scratches.  

The Perfect iPad Cover features a button and elastic band closure which will keep your iPad safe and secure.

name: Crayon Pouch - Purple & Blue
description:
Crayon Pouches are a great accessory for little ones! 

Crayon Pouches have a ribbon handle that is approximately 3 inches long making them easy for little hands to carry. Each pouch holds 7 crayons and come with a new box of crayola crayons and 1 notepad to get the creativity started.

Crayon Pouches are large enough to hold a few extra toys as well making them versatile. Bring them shopping, to restaurants, church, on vacation or to use around the house.

Crayon Pouch is 7.5 inches wide by 7 inches high 
Made with Joel Dewberry Heirloom Fabric

Hand wash and lay flat to dry

name: Reversible Market Tote - Rose Boquet
description:
The Reversible Market Tote is a great addition to your everyday style.  They look great heading to the office, shopping and along side a stroller.

Each tote is made using coordinating designer fabrics which look great inside and out.   They are approximately 16" tall and 18" wide with 1" wide and 22" long chocolate brown leather handles.  All edges are double stitched for extra durability.

The Reversible Market Tote would make a lovely gift bag filled with Sew Jules goodies.

Spot clean tote with a damp cloth and allow to air dry.
